process of knowledge exchange and cooperative production on the internet/web itself. But there are many
specialized inititiaves to construct specialized areas, such as initiatives around access to scientific journals, the
creation of specialized Intellectual Property licenses to promote it, such as the General Public License and the
Creative Commons License, and a massive effort to put the world's literary and scientific book production
online.<br />
